item.title: CVE-2023-32261|2023-07-19T15:56:25.049Z -- micro%20focus -- dimensions%20cm
item.description: A potential vulnerability has been identified in the Micro Focus Dimensions CM Plugin for Jenkins. The vulnerability allows attackers with Overall/Read permission to enumerate credentials IDs of credentials stored in Jenkins. See the following Jenkins security advisory for details: * https://www.jenkins.io/security/advisory/2023-06-14/ https://www.jenkins.io/security/advisory/2023-06-14/
